# Studio Frontend (`apps/web`)

## Feature layout

```
src/features/
  studio/     Timeline, canvas (Konva), tools dock, filmstrip, export
  translation/  Gemini AI transcribe/translate/voiceover
  project/    useAppStore (Zustand) — single project state
  upload/     Video upload flow
  settings/   Theme, i18n preferences
```

## Studio tools (CapCut-style rail)

`media | text | audio | voice | captions | effects | transitions | filters`

- Presets from `useEditorCatalog()` + apply via `useEditorActions()`.
- Filter preview: CSS on `<video>` via `getVideoCssFilter()` in store.
- Server apply/preview when `videoSessionId` exists (`useVideoSession` on studio load).

## State

- **useAppStore**: video file, timeline, canvas elements, `projectEditor` (filters, caption style, clip transitions).
- **Server session**: `videoSessionId` set after `api.createVideoSession()`; cleared on new video.

## API client

```typescript
import { api } from '@/lib/api/client';
// Dev proxy: /api → gateway :4000 (see vite.config.ts)
```

## UI

- Import components from `@vokop/ui` or `@/components/ui` (re-export).
- Button hover: color/opacity only — no transform scale/translate (see `button-interactions` rule).
